Unit 5

types of mode of php

1. copy mode
2. interpret mode

Before that tag we have copy mode
when compiler finds <? php    tag it enters into interpret mode
after ?> tag where php ends

we come back to copy mode


Data types

1. scalar : integer, double, boolean, string
2. composite : arrays, objects
3. null & resource


